<HEAD>New Probe Of Company Suspected In Libya Plant Scandal</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: Retransmitting to restore Bjt designation</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TERRENCE PETTY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BONN, West Germany (AP) </DATELINE>
